marytts.signalproc.filter
Class ComplementaryFilterBankChannelAnalyser

java.lang.Object
  marytts.signalproc.filter.ComplementaryFilterBankChannelAnalyser

public class ComplementaryFilterBankChannelAnalyser
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements a single channel of the complementary filter bank used in [Levine, et. al., 1999] for multiresolution sinusoidal modeling. [Levine, et. al., 1999] Levine, S. N., Verma, T. S., and Smith III, J. O., "Multiresolution sinusoidal modeling for wideband audio with modifications", in Proc. of the IEEE ICASSP 1998, Volume 6, Issue , 12-15 May 1998, pp. 3585-3588.

Author:
Oytun Türk
